ambitious though double-edged way of handling the position:} 19. exf5 Bxf5 20.
Qb3+ Kh8 21. Rbd1 Qf4 22. Nc3 Bd4 $5 23. Qxb7 Bxc5 24. Bf3 $13 {with a complex
